In this folder, there are 4 files: 

1) rho_estimation.R contains the main function for estimation of rho using auxiliarly covariates Z

2) TWINS_rho.R contains detailed code for estimation of rho, hat(rho) and tilde(hat(rho)) in this dataset

3) sim_rho_est_high_dim and 4) sim_rho_estimation_univariate contain details about the experiments regarding  hat(rho) estimation in the appendix of the manuscript. 



